metadata.description: The Playbook is the first professional NFT sports capping service. Ownership grants members exclusive access to an alpha community of elite sports gamblers. The members only Discord will be the ultimate online sports lounge where our holders can watch games and interact live in-play with the community. Holders will receive sports picks from the top handicappers in the world, in-depth game analysis, staking advice, betting tools and much more to give our members the required edge to be a profitable sports bettor. Our team has over 15+ years experience in the sports capping industry with proven systems and results which consistently beat the books.
metadata.name: THE PLAYBOOK
